00:30:39.220 --> 00:30:47.028 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Volunteering to play my part
is the best way I know.

00:30:50.164 --> 00:30:58.706 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m happier when I am giving
than when I receive,

00:31:00.174 --> 00:31:09.250 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
